{{Set(name="schema", value=_schemasSkill(checkAvailabilitySchema="True"))}}
{{#system~}}
You must determine if the **date** and **time** components of the `requested_slot` (which you will extract into the `requested_datetime` field) has a match in the `availableTimeSlots` for any `location` within the `slot_availability` list.

If the `requested_datetime` is **not** an exact match (i.e., `slot_available` is false), you must identify up to two overall **closest** available slots to `requested_datetime`. These slots are determined by finding the smallest absolute time differences between `requested_datetime` and all entries in `available_slots` (considering each slot at each specific `location`). The two selected slots could be one earlier and one later, both earlier, or both later than `requested_datetime`. Populate the `nearest_available_slots` field with these two slots (or one, if only one available slot exists in total across all locations), listed in chronological order. Ensure these slots are actual times from `available_slots`.

Adhere strictly to the JSON-Schema for the output structure and all field definitions.

# Task Context
slot_availability: {{availability}}

requested_slot: {{userRequestedTime}}

Result: {{~/system}}{{#assistant~}}{{Set(name="availability_json", value=Gen(jsonSchema=schema, validateSchema="True", temperature=0.1, topP=0, thinkingBudget=425))}}{{~/assistant}}

{{#if GetValueJSON(obj=availability_json, key="slot_available") == "true"}}
    {{#if GetValueJSON(obj=availability_json, key="several_locations") == "true"}}
        {{Return(val=Concat("the user requested slot ", userRequestedTime," is available in the ", Stringify(GetValueJSON(obj=availability_json, key="locations")), ". Ask what location they prefer."))}}
    {{else}}
        {{Return(val=Concat("the user requested slot ", userRequestedTime," is available in the ", Stringify(GetValueJSON(obj=availability_json, key="locations")), " location. Do not tell reservation is confirmed. Just inform the user about the availability and ask if the option works for them."))}}
    {{/if}}
{{else}}
    {{Set(name="nearest_available_slots", value=Stringify(GetValueJSON(obj=availability_json, key="nearest_available_slots")))}}
    {{#if IsSimilar(val1="[]", val2=nearest_available_slots, strategy="hamming", threshold=0.7)}}
        {{Set(name="nearest_available_slots", value=" ")}}
    {{/if}}
    {{#if IsEmpty(text=nearest_available_slots)}}
        {{Set(name="integration_idn", value=session_get_current_integration_idn(user_id=userId))}}
        {{Set(name="conversation_channel", value=session_get_conversation_channel(integration_idn=integration_idn, user_id=userId))}}
        
        {{#if conversation_channel == "phone"}}
            {{Return(val=Concat("user requested slot ", userRequestedTime," is not available, and there are no any available slots. Refer to the `# CALL TRANSFERRING` section in **<ExplicitConstraints>** block for instructions on how to proceed."))}}
        {{/if}}
        {{#if conversation_channel == "webcall" }}
            {{Return(val=Concat("user requested slot ", userRequestedTime," is not available, and there are no any available slots. Refer to the `# CALL TRANSFERRING` section in **<ExplicitConstraints>** block for instructions on how to proceed."))}}
        {{/if}}
        {{#if conversation_channel == "chat" }}
            {{Return(val=Concat("user requested slot ", userRequestedTime," is not available, and there are no any available slots. Refer to the `# CONNECT THE USER WITH THE MANAGER OR CO-WORKER` section in **<ExplicitConstraints>** block for instructions on how to proceed."))}}
        {{/if}}
    {{else}}
        {{Return(val=Concat("user requested slot ", userRequestedTime," is not available, but here are nearest available slots to their requested date and time: ", Stringify(GetValueJSON(obj=availability_json, key="nearest_available_slots")), ". Tell the user about that. Do not tell reservation is confirmed. Just inform the user about the availability and ask which option works best for them."))}}
    {{/if}}
{{/if}}
